{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-js","path":"/drupal-locale-block/","result":{"data":{"remark":{"fields":{"path":"drupal-locale-block"},"meta":{"title":""},"headings":[{"value":"Drupal Locale Block"}],"html":"<h1>Drupal Locale Block</h1>\n<p>Если на главной странице отображается конкретная нода, то блок <strong>locale</strong> (отображающий доступные языки сайта), на главной странице не работает</p>\n<p>Проблема лечиться в файле: <code class=\"language-text\">/modules/locale/locale.module</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre class=\"language-php\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">//$path = drupal_is_front_page() ? '&lt;front>' : $_GET['q'];</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$path</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">drupal_is_front_page</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'node'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token function\">arg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'&lt;front>'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$_GET</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'q'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},"pageContext":{"id":"87e6a1f0-bc24-5826-9630-182947c5cc2b"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}